reviews.text:
This restaurant situates at TST Peninsula Centre but the centre has nothing to do with Peninsula Hotel which is quite a distance away. 
The restaurant offers Chinese hotpots and other Chinese cuisines. Prices are reasonable and commensurate with the quality of food. You can try greasy goose. It is not often crowded and may give you a short period of peace if you are going to dine there.
Just another Chinese Restaurant in Hong Kong out of the approximately 12000 of them
CP值高。尖沙咀區火鍋任食好選擇
好味新鮮， 生蝦 ，手打麻辣牛丸 ，必食。
與朋友慶生晚飯，小菜不錯亦不貴，服務員態度都很好。

reviews.text: This is a good hot pot buffet, the price is big and clean. around 20 choise varieties and some food out side get it yourself.  the meat and sea food can order include,  highly recommend with  family and friends , and they have 4 hours to eat. only $199 per people.

Dinner: $199/person all u can eat hotpot and drink (soda) from sun to thus, $20 more on fri and sat. 10% service charge applies. No additional cost on broth unless u order the special ones. Place is big and clean, generous variety of food. No time limit, u can sit till they close. Definitely a hidden gem, would definitely be back.
Extra: MTR fare saver stationed at the same building ($2 off your next ride of MTR same day if u tap your octopus card)
Many seats but too many tour for lunch. Food is OK, Monday to Friday with around 80% discount . Attach seafood thick white noodle original $82 but discount to$68

We came for the Steamboat/ hot pot buffet. Well worth the price. Tons of varieties and the base pork bone soup which we ordered was so good. Highly recommended. Ingredients are fresh as well. Though service can be abit slower than usual depending on the crowd
Chinese hot pot  (buffet or order per dish) in Tsim Sha Tsui East. Hong Kong. Acceptable price

result.name: Tack Hsin Restaurant

reviews.text:
這家酒樓有多年歷史 證明有實力才屹立至今
這一次和家人到這裡食個火鍋~

發現有不限時HKD$199任食(加一服務費)
這裡的環境挻大的 去到的時候不多人
但過了一會兒就坐無虛席🤪🤪🤪

我們也很快地下單點東西食
先來一個鴛鴦鍋湯底 可以食到2個味道

·肩胛牛肉眼
·金錢展
·羊肉卷
·竹串海生蝦
·豬潤
·花膠仔
·帶子片
·黑豚肉卷
·白鱔片
·水晶奶黃
·半殼青口

我們也點了好多款食物來食耶🤤🤤
食材也挻新鮮的 種類也不算少😬😬

自助食物/飲品吧還有其他火鍋配
酸梅湯我拿了2大枝來和家人飲🤫

令我印象最深刻的食物是水晶奶黃
原本以為是甜點來的 原來是火鍋配料來[笑哭]
經過淥熟後 外皮挻晶瑩剔透的
入面的奶黃很Creamy及滑身 
我們點了好幾個食物來食呢^^
連鎖中式餐廳，可吃中業。夜晚建議吃放題火鍋，價錢經濟。
今天到訪(星期六)，好快有位原因🤷‍♀️今天所食的点心、蚊米，味道適中😅
